p.d: From Grammy winners to those just starting out, Soul & Jazz LIVE! features artists from around the world performing original material captured as part of a live recorded studio session. Episode 4 includes Michael J McEvoy, Maurice Brown, Resolution 88, Lindsey Webster, Bill Laurance, Pocket Dragon, YolanDa Brown, Harleighblu, and Simon Lasky. Produced by Spacerocket Media for SoulandJazz.com, this is the fourth in a six-part series featuring performances captured since late 2016.
